@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>Electricity</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
            <h3>Spot Market Analysis</h3>
            <p>
                Various key observations about the supply and demand system curves (such as sensitivity analysis).
                Supply curve generation components, marginal costs and other relevant analytics.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/EnergyMarkets/SpotCurvesAnalysis">Supply & Demand Analysis &raquo;</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Short-term Price Forecasting</h3>
            <p>
                High accuracy period-ahead price forecasting based on a multivariate model including a wide array of
                variables(e.g. production, wind, gas) based on flexible parameters and multiple approaches.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/EnergyMarkets/SpotPriceForecast">Day-Ahead Forecast &raquo;</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Spot Price Simulation</h3>
            <p>
                Modelling and simulation of all foward market (forward contracts) based on a model
                that matches information from the whole structure (e.g. options, emissions) and multiple time resolutions.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/EnergyMarkets/ForwardMarketAnalysis">Spot Price Simulation &raquo;</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Wind Park Valuation</h3>
            <p>
                A simulation model that calculates the value of a wind park assuming its power is sold partly via
                a broker on the spot market.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/EnergyMarkets/PowerPurchaseAgreement">Wind Park Valuation &raquo;</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>Gas</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
            <h3>Forward Curve Simulation</h3>
            <p>
                An advanced model providing flexibility to simulation of the forward curve, in includes a dynamic term structure, underlying
                model flexibility and a variety of nice features such as drag-and-drop interactions and a simple interface.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/GasMarkets/ForwardCurves">Forward Curve Simulation... &raquo;</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>Cross-commodities</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
            <h3>Virtual Power Plant</h3>
            <p>
                A simple demonstration of a virtual power plant using a multi-fuel that relies on real time data
                and highly customizable parameters.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/RiskManagement/PlantPortfolio">VPP &raquo;</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

